KitKat::

She followed Perceptor into the recieving chamber of Hydrus.  She 
looked up at the bot. He appeared to be a formaidable bot.  She 
bowed to him and showed the proper respect. 
"I am KitKat. I am at your service." 

She stood at proper military parade rest, hands behind her back and 
tail motionless behind her.  She kept her optics on her new leader. 
Preds never truely trust anybot. It's against thier programming. She 
was however aware of the other bots and kept an ear out for them.
